  "texts": [
    "We use a system based on scaled YOLOv4 to offer a real-time sign language detection model.",
    "Our main goal is to provide real-time detection by optimally adjusting the scaling parameters in the backbone and neck of the model.",
    "We add transformers [35] to the scaled YOLOv4 architecture to improve the performance of our proposed detection model.",
    "An important study on transformer architecture is recommended by Vaswani et al.",
    "Transformer, which consists of an encoder-decoder architecture, is based on a system that works entirely with an attention mechanism instead of a traditional recurrent neural network to increase the training speed of the network."
  ],
